Pretty good. We used mangos and blueberries instead of pears and raspberries (late March isn't really the best time of the year for fruit). Enjoyed the honey and rum combo, but used only a half teaspoon of the bitters. Anything more than that would have been overkill. For fruit salad, it's very dark tasting and full of warm flavors, so I'd consider using brighter, more tropical fruits next time.

