Everyone really enjoyed this dish, yes I did change some of the fruits using pineapple, mango, apple, nectarines, red & green seedless grapes, and a mix of blueberries, raspberries and blackberries. The dressing makes the dish. I used only 2 tbsp of honey, thought it might be too sweet and added a tbsp of freshely squeezed meyer lemon juice (helped keep the fruit from discoloring) Was a big hit at easter brunch! A definite keeper

